---
import InnerPage from '../../components/InnerPage.astro';
const lang = 'en' as const;
---
<InnerPage lang={lang} path="/services" title="Services — Ostvera" description="Sourcing, quality control, registration, EAEU, customs, logistics and service." heading="Services" kicker="Ostvera">
  <p class="lead">The full cycle of medical equipment supply from China &mdash; stage by stage, each handled by us.</p>
  <h3>Sourcing at factories</h3>
  <p>We find equipment to your requirements and budget at vetted Chinese manufacturers and prepare a quote.</p>
  <h3>Supplier audit and quality control</h3>
  <p>We check the production, inspect the batch and accept samples before shipment.</p>
  <h3>Registration and EAEU certification</h3>
  <p>We support obtaining the Roszdravnadzor registration certificate and prepare EAEU declarations and certificates of conformity.</p>
  <h3>Foreign trade and customs</h3>
  <p>HS codes, import VAT, customs clearance and cargo insurance.</p>
  <h3>Logistics</h3>
  <p>Rail, air, sea and road &mdash; we match the route to timeline and budget.</p>
  <h3>Service and spare parts</h3>
  <p>Warranty, spare parts, consumables and staff training &mdash; in Russia.</p>
</InnerPage>
